"Verificación & [cm; cm; rad]
'<hr/>
E = 2100000*kgf/cm^2
A = 100*cm^2
I = 5000*cm^4
L = 400*cm

k1 = E*A/L
k2 = 12*E*I/L^3
k3 = 6*E*I/L^2
k4 = 4*E*I/L

K = [k1; 0*kgf/cm; 0*kgf | 0*kgf/cm; k2; k3 | 0*kgf; k3; k4]

'<h4>F calculado manualmente: F = K*[0.1cm; 0.05cm; 0.001rad]</h4>
'F1 = k1*0.1 = 52500 kgf
'F2 = k2*0.05 + k3*0.001 = ... kgf
'F3 = k3*0.05 + k4*0.001 = ... kgf·cm
F1 = k1*0.1*cm
F2 = k2*0.05*cm + k3*0.001
F3 = k3*0.05*cm + k4*0.001

F1
F2
F3

F_v = [F1; F2; F3]

'<h4>Resolver</h4>
u = lsolve(K; F_v) & [cm; cm; rad]
u
